OL,3,CChild saved after dangling from window
OL,4,Cledge above shop in east London
OL,6,FA child has been dramatically rescued
OL,7,Fafter dangling from window above a
OL,8,Fshop in Ilford. Footage shows the
OL,9,Fyoung girl clinging to a ledge as a
OL,10,Fcrowd gathers on the street below.
OL,12,FA woman is seen reaching up to help
OL,13,Fbefore a police officer appears
OL,14,Ffollowed by another man who catches
OL,15,Fthe girl as she falls.
OL,17,FThe child appears to hit her feet on a
OL,18,Fledge but safely ends up in the arms
OL,19,Fof her rescuer and is checked by the
OL,20,Fofficer.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
