OL,3,CChild saved after dangling from window
OL,4,Cledge above shop in east London
OL,6,FThe girl appeared to climb out of an
OL,7,Fopen window above a pawnbrokers shop.
OL,9,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,10,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,11,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,12,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News London, the
OL,15,Fgirl's rescuer, Mohamad Jesin
OL,16,Fexplained how the drama unfolded:
OL,17,F"There were so many people standing
OL,18,Ftaking videos.
OL,20,F"She was hanging there and lost her
OL,21,Fgrip."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/3
