OL,3,CChild saved after dangling from window
OL,4,Cledge above shop in east London
OL,6,FAsked how he felt when Mohamad caught
OL,7,Fher he said: "Happy, happy for her.
OL,8,FShe hugged me."
OL,10,FMohamad said he didn't feel like a
OL,11,Fhero but just did what he had to do.
